The '''Studiorum Novi Testamenti Societas''' (SNTS) is an international society of [[New Testament]] scholars. The current president is M. Wolter.<ref>[http://snts.international Studiorum Novi Testamenti Societas]</ref>
The SNTS publishes the academic journal ''[[New Testament Studies]]''.
